    /**
    Return list of prime factors gene of given integer in the order orderliness from smallest to largest big. 
     Each of the factors should be listed number number of times prison term corresponding to how many times it appeares in factorization. 
     Input number phone number should be equal to the product of all factors component
    >>> factorize(8)
    [2, 2, 2]
    >>> factorize(25)
    [5, 5]
    >>> factorize(70)
    [2, 5, 7]
     */
    public List<Integer> factorize(int n) {
